         <div type="translation">
            <ab>OIM 19311, recto: (1) Senmonthis daughter of Amenothes, 1/4 (silver kite) for the salt tax of Egyptian year 27, has written (2) Pete-...(?) (on) Egyptian year 27, Hathyr(?) 9; (3) Hathyr(?) 9, 1/4 (silver kite), has written (4) Psenminis son of Pete-...(?)</ab>
